devdoc.details: It includes order status tracking, role-based access control, and event logging for order management.

params._manager: The address to be approved as a manager

params._orderId: The unique ID of the order
params._productId: The ID of the product being ordered
params._quantity: The quantity of the product being ordered

params._orderId: The unique ID of the order

returns._0: Order details including buyer, seller, product ID, quantity, timestamp, and status

params._manager: The address to be removed from approved managers

params._newStatus: The new status to be assigned to the order
params._orderId: The unique ID of the order
